  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::JournalData
  id: 38
  title: "Ghi ch\xE9p thu\u1ED1c gi\u1EA3i #2 \u2014 B\u1EC7nh nh\xE2n 001"
  category: 6
  content: "Ghi ch\xE9p cu\u1ED1i. B\u1EC7nh nh\xE2n 001 \u2014 ch\xEDnh l\xE0 ng\u01B0\u1EDDi
    anh trai c\u1EE7a m\u1ED9t thanh ni\xEAn \u0111ang t\xECm anh trong th\xE0nh
    ph\u1ED1. Anh ta t\xECnh nguy\u1EC7n th\u1EED thu\u1ED1c gi\u1EA3i prototype.
    L\u1EA7n th\u1EED \u0111\u1EA7u: s\u1ED1t cao, co gi\u1EADt, nh\u01B0ng kh\xF4ng
    bi\u1EBFn. L\u1EA7n th\u1EED hai: m\u1EAFt tr\u1EDF l\u1EA1i b\xECnh th\u01B0\u1EDDng,
    nh\u1EADn th\u1EE9c r\xF5. Nh\u01B0ng r\u1ED3i thu\u1ED1c b\u1ECB m\u1EA5t \u2014
    b\u1ECB qu\xE2n \u0111\u1ED9i t\u1ECBch thu khi r\xFAt lui. Anh ta v\u1EABn c\xF2n
    s\u1ED1ng, \u0111ang \u1EA9n \u1EDF \u0111\xE2u \u0111\xF3 trong t\xF2a cao t\u1EA7ng.
    N\u1EBFu em anh \u0111\u1ECDc \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c: anh v\u1EABn c\xF2n s\u1ED1ng.
    T\xECm anh \u1EDF t\u1EA7ng cao nh\u1EA5t."
  image: {fileID: 0}
  voiceLog: {fileID: 0}
